273
00:16:06,725 --> 00:16:07,857
Minha esposa.

274
00:16:07,859 --> 00:16:09,392
Ei, Kat.

275
00:16:09,394 --> 00:16:10,727
<i>Onde você está?</i>

276
00:16:10,729 --> 00:16:12,695
